ZH: 公交车是我每天上下班的主要交通工具。
EN: The bus is my main mode of transportation to and from work every day.

ZH: 我通常乘坐公交车去商场。
EN: I usually take the bus to go to the mall.

ZH: 妈妈让我坐公交车去学校。
EN: My mom told me to take the bus to school.

ZH: 公交车上的座位已经全部被占了。
EN: All the seats on the bus are already taken.

ZH: 我总是迟到，因为经常赶不上公交车。
EN: I'm always late because I often miss the bus.

ZH: 今天下雨了，公交车上的人都用伞遮雨。
EN: It's raining today, and people on the bus are using umbrellas to shield themselves from the rain.

ZH: 公交车司机是一个很友好的人。
EN: The bus driver is a very friendly person.

ZH: 公交车上的人们都在手机上玩游戏。
EN: The people on the bus are all playing games on their phones.

ZH: 公交车上的座位非常舒适。
EN: The seats on the bus are very comfortable.

ZH: 这辆公交车上有一个非常大的广告牌。
EN: There is a very large billboard on this bus.

ZH: 我得去车站等公交车。
EN: I have to go to the bus stop to wait for the bus.

ZH: 公交车上的空调开得很凉快。
EN: The air conditioning on the bus is very cool.

ZH: 公交车上的乘客都在聊天。
EN: The passengers on the bus are all chatting.

ZH: 我们可以坐公交车去公园。
EN: We can take the bus to the park.

ZH: 公交车经过市中心。
EN: The bus goes through the city center.

ZH: 我不喜欢在拥挤的公交车上站着。
EN: I don't like standing on a crowded bus.

ZH: 公交车开得非常快。
EN: The bus is driving very fast.

ZH: 我在公交车上遇到了一个老朋友。
EN: I ran into an old friend on the bus.

ZH: 别忘了带上公交卡。
EN: Don't forget to bring your bus pass.

ZH: 公交车上的座位很干净。
EN: The seats on the bus are very clean.
